{
  "stem": "24212.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that leads me to mention a little episode during the war, what the resistance did-- put laxative in-- in the coffee of the Nazis.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I though this was a Czech invention, which is far from the truth, because I talk to people in Greece and Norway and points in between.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They all did the same thing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The human mind works, to a large degree, the same way, nationality or no nationality.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Very easy item on the list of resistors-- put laxatives in their coffee.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Unfortunately we didn't see the result, you know, how they were holding their tummies and running, you know.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But that happened all over the place.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I started being aware of that when they actively did something.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't see, for instance-- well, I heard that in Germany, for instance, the-- the Jews could not be doctors or lawyers or professors, and so on.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But it was sort of like when you hear thunder far in the background.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was too young to care, probably.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And you know, the town where I was was given to Hungary, as at Munich the Sudetenland was given to the Germans.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And so the Hungarians said, and we want the southern part of Slovakia.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So Kosice went Hungarian.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the Hungarian Jews were relatively very lucky, because trouble-- real serious trouble for life in Hungary didn't start until Eichmann came to Hungary on March 19.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "That's Saint Joseph's Day.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "That's how I remember the date.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he started the ball rolling in Hungary.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "By that time I was long gone.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
